    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Screening wet sediment in plastic state for aggregate particles larger than a certain size. In construction, refers to removal of particles from fresh concrete. In archaeology, a method of recovering animal and plant remains from archaeological deposits.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
